inputs.text: A surreal alien landscape with two skeletal figures sitting atop cracked, glowing orbs covered in strange organic textures. The sky is filled with swirling, otherworldly hues of orange and brown, with distant planets visible. The skeletons wear mushroom-like growths on their heads and cloaks, blending eerily with the alien environment, evoking a hauntingly mystical, sci-fi vibe.
